{"tid":897711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「光復東涌」打擊黑工導遊 親中團體踩場爆混亂","createTime":"2018-11-11T07:08:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-14T03:21:49.000Z","uid":39464,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9290c3b3ee954f27a91645f9345e2bfec295f023","tid":897711,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T07:08:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181111/large/1541919100_f4e3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181111%2Flarge%2F1541919100_f4e3.jpg&h=3c1d827b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港珠澳大橋通車後，東涌成為內地遊客的「落腳點」，昨日為通車後第三個周末，入境處公佈昨日共有9.2萬人次經大橋香港口岸出入境，比對上一個周六多五千多人。早前被指大排長龍影響當區居民、往大橋香港口岸的B6巴士站，巴士公司繼續於站頭架起鐵馬，並加派職員在場協助。<br />\n<br />\n傘後組織「東涌人」今日下午2時30分發起「光復東涌」行動，表示會尋找黑工導遊並主動舉報，以打擊「不明來歷旅行團」，但他們強調不會不會針對遵守秩序的旅客。親中團體「珍惜群組」亦到場「踩場」，於東涌港鐵站外擺檔支持大橋通車，並高呼「本是同根生、陸港一家親」口號，批評反對者的目的是為了「搞分裂」、「撕裂香港」。他們又稱有人「冒警」檢查旅行團導遊牌照，稱會要求律政司執法。期間有反對者用粗口指罵，有警員上前阻止。<br />\n<br />\n「光復行動」發起人王進洋下午2時35分於東涌站A出口起步，到B6巴士站監察是否有違規旅行團，期間「龍心」林克霖「踩場」，以粗言指罵王進洋「尋日做乜搞X我老頂周浩鼎呀？」<br />\n<br />\n港珠澳大橋上月底通車，大批遊客迫爆東涌，東涌居民生活大受影響。運輸署急忙推出分流措施補鑊，包括宣傳B6線以外巴士，及設團體登記處等。港珠澳大橋入境大堂巴士站今日人潮明顯減少，未見往日迫爆情景。不過旅行團大多仍選擇乘搭往東涌的B6巴士，每車坐滿旅行團客，約百人排隊。B6巴士站頭，有工作人員協助旅客處理票務及管理上車秩序，因班次頻密，人龍消化速度較快。<br />\n<br />\n居於東堤灣畔逾10年的梁小姐稱，當初搬入東涌是因為環境寧靜，但自大橋通車後，大量旅客湧入，「越整越過分」。她又指「睇唔過眼」珍惜群組今日到場支持擾民行為。<br />\n梁小姐指大陸旅客坐姿不雅、亂拋垃圾，但她認為問題源頭是政府政策安排不當。她又表示曾經向當區區議員反映，但只獲回覆「做緊嘢」。她又稱會在日後業主立案法團會議等場合提出意見。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181111/large/1541914378_90a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181111%2Flarge%2F1541914378_90a4.png&h=6a06d18d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181111/large/1541919099_5714.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181111%2Flarge%2F1541919099_5714.jpg&h=8335b57e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181111/large/1541913776_fca5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181111%2Flarge%2F1541913776_fca5.jpg&h=ef375c02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181111/large/1541913778_a8b9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181111%2Flarge%2F1541913778_a8b9.jpg&h=133c1104&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181111/large/1541913777_38f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181111%2Flarge%2F1541913777_38f2.jpg&h=1418ed8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181111/large/1541909221_bc72.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181111%2Flarge%2F1541909221_bc72.jpg&h=ed21b9b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181111/58899831\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181111%2F58899831&d=nU4zFllnu80LzyJiqHEC%2BMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=b609c6f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181111%2F58899831&h=a66c1bc9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181111/58899831</a>"},{"pid":"2bd5f1d5f825f6669a2c71c1940f521df72fb069","tid":897711,"uid":2090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T07:10:05.000Z","msg":"龍心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb89038ca843b9229a41a6622462228bcfcb3cb2","tid":897711,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-1