ass=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 住市區"},{"pid":"2cb0ddf03182391a01cee737f217288c564d3608","tid":897711,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T03:12:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2588704656b4144af2254303d2c1737e004ec488","tid":897711,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T03:16:27.000Z","msg":"播放國歌<br />\n邊個唔企正record 佢, 放上百度公審<br />\n<br />\n港共未立法, 仍可以周街播<br />\n不過佢地要遵守返全國法律<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一表現出唔尊重可以拉去勞改再打靶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"780622ad1d9de7ccf74299f087d6436a47925269","tid":897711,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T03:21:49.000Z","msg":"誠意邀請五毛狙擊手#38523星期日2018Nov18同我一齊光復東涌<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/bMBupS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/bMBupS</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}